# --- Secrets & local env (Sprint 0 hardening; Safe Backend Doctrine principle 1) ---
# Never commit real secret values. Values live in the Cloudflare Pages env/secret store
# (prod) and .dev.vars locally. Commit .env.example (NAMES only) instead.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
site/.env
site/.env.*
!site/.env.example
*.key
*.pem
API_KEY.txt
SHOTSTACK_KEYS.txt
.mcp.json
.dev.vars
site/.dev.vars
.wrangler/
site/.wrangler/

# Email-list backups: real subscriber PII, must never be committed here (script also refuses)
gotefigure-email-backups/
